gov.usgs.traveltime.tables

Class ModelInterp

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.traveltime.tables.ModelInterp

  • public class ModelInterp
extends java.lang.Object
    Interpolate the model. This encapsulation is necessary because the Apache Commons library routines don't handle the zero length intervals used in the Earth models to flag discontinuities in velocity.
